title: Tangerine Dream - The Dream Roots Collection
description:
Tangerine Dream - The Dream Roots Collection [5CD Box Set] (1996)
MP3 CBR 320 kbps (LAME 3.93) 
Genre: Electronic, Berlin School

The Dream Roots Collection is a five-disc retrospective of Tangerine Dream's career, including one disc of previously unreleased material. All of the material on the collection has been remixed and reworked by Edgar Froese and his son Jerome, and while these remixes might not be historically accurate, they nevertheless retain the essence of the original versions, making the box an intriguing journey through the group's past.
